Just moments after he'd been celebrating Jake Quickenden's 10-star performance in the live Bush Tucker Trial on Sunday, Jimmy Bullard was back in the thick of it.

Thinking he was immune from facing a challenge for at least another day, the former Wigan man was shocked when asked to take part in a bonus trial for an extra treat.

Reluctantly, the 36-year-old followed Quickenden's lead and faced the Critter Cube - part two.

