A terrified looking Jimmy was told he would have to put his hand in a box of three snakes.

In reference to one of Bullard's previous tasks involving snakes, host Ant McPartlin joked: 'That last snake didn't like you...it's not the same snake.'

To which his partner-in-crime Declan Donelly quipped: 'But they've been talking to the other snake!'

